"I just got of back from church pretty good- -AYE. But it doesn't take long to learn that there's no atheists riding in airplanes not on this side of the pond. One realizes more every day that there is someone up above l
ooking after you and he really has been doing a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5906035  good job." (414th Bomb Sq., APO}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2303636  520).
